SELECT * FROM coaching_sessions WHERE session_type = 'Group' ORDER BY session_date DESC;

SELECT client_name, client_organization, coach_name FROM clients c JOIN coaching_sessions cs ON c.client_id = cs.session_id JOIN coaches co ON cs.coach_id = co.coach_id WHERE co.coaching_experience > 5;
SELECT coach_name, AVG(session_duration) AS avg_duration FROM coaches JOIN coaching_sessions ON coaches.coach_id = coaching_sessions.coach_id GROUP BY coach_name ORDER BY avg_duration DESC;

SELECT coach_name, COUNT(*) AS session_count FROM coaches JOIN coaching_sessions ON coaches.coach_id = coaching_sessions.coach_id WHERE coaching_sessions.session_date BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2022-12-31' GROUP BY coach_name HAVING session_count > 3;
SELECT client_name, COUNT(*) AS total_sessions FROM clients c JOIN coaching_sessions cs ON c.client_id = cs.client_id GROUP BY client_name ORDER BY total_sessions DESC LIMIT 5;

SELECT coach_name, session_date FROM coaching_sessions WHERE session_duration > '01:00:00';

SELECT c.first_name AS client_name, s.session_date, t.topic_name FROM clients c JOIN coaching_sessions s ON c.client_id = s.client_id JOIN coaching_topics t ON s.coach_id = t.coach_id;
SELECT s.session_id, s.session_date, f.feedback_text FROM coaching_sessions s LEFT JOIN session_feedback f ON s.session_id = f.session_id WHERE f.rating >= 4;
